summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Tilo Live single-page website conversion. All backend APIs (11/11) and frontend functionality working perfectly. Single-page navigation, hero section with salary table, 3 salary tables, benefits section, rules section, contact form, admin panel, and mobile responsiveness all functional.
passed_tests: Public settings API returns correct data
Contact form submission saves to database
Hero section loads with salary sheet table (10 rows)
Salary section displays 3 tables: Diamond Salary (8 rows), Fixed Salary (5 rows), Agency Salary (7 rows)
Benefits section displays new host benefits, settlement details, and 3 earning method cards
Rules section shows call rejection timeline, host level badges, and perfect host split cards
Contact form submission integrates with backend
WhatsApp float button present and functional
